{
  "name": "Lightning Release Electromagnetic Annoyance",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Lightning.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You conjure your lightning release chakra to generate a wave of electricity. Each creature in a 20-foot cube originating from you must succeed a Constitution saving throw being Shocked until the end of their next turn on a failed save. If a creature is already shocked, they make this save at disadvantage.</p><p>A creature who is shocked and gains another rank of shock as a result of this jutsu has their shocked condition duration increased to 1 minute.</p><p>Overcharge. When you cast this jutsu, as a bonus action or reaction, you can overcharge its effects. When you do, all creatures who fail their saving throw have their speed reduced by 10 for the duration of the shocked condition.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the cube by 5 feet.</p>",
